title: International Space Banana Directly Download
description:
I don’t know what happened, but man , I’m a banana. And I can move like a banana. I can rotate through zero gravity like only a banana can. I can latch onto things with my banana body. Thank the lord I am not a kiwi. If I were a kiwi I wouldn’t be able to swing my weight around like this and move. The Walking Dead
And I mean to be honest it feels great. This is nice. I’m a nice yellow banana. No bruises. I’m actually a pretty attractive banana. I feel like one of I feel like the best banana in the bunch. I FEEL LIKE THE BEST BANANA IN THE BUNCH But I’m the only banana in the bunch Where is everyone?”
